  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_68_14495-14518",
      "chapterUid": 68,
      "range": "14495-14518",
      "markText": "鹤寿千岁，以极其游；蜉蝣朝生而暮死，而尽其乐。",
      "totalCount": 850,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=68&rangeStart=14495&rangeEnd=14518",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=68&rangeStart=14495&rangeEnd=14518"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_94-144",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "94-144",
      "markText": "在自然之道的滋润指导下，人类要保持“清静”、“无为”的信念，保养精神、守住形气，达到恬淡自满的境界。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=94&rangeEnd=144",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=94&rangeEnd=144"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_5566-5659",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "5566-5659",
      "markText": "夫井鱼不可与语大，拘于隘也；夏虫不可与语寒，笃于时也；曲士不可与语至道，拘于俗，束于教也。故圣人不以人滑天，不以欲乱情，不谋而当，不言而信，不虑而得，不为而成，精通于灵府，与造化者为人。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=5566&rangeEnd=5659",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=5566&rangeEnd=5659"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_7244-7286",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "7244-7286",
      "markText": "夫善游者溺，善骑者堕。各以其所好，反自为祸。是故好事者未尝不中①，争利者未尝不穷也。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=7244&rangeEnd=7286",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=7244&rangeEnd=7286"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_8_452-506",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "452-506",
      "markText": "昔者共工与颛顼争为帝，怒而触不周之山，天柱折，地维绝。天倾西北，故日月星辰移焉；地不满东南，故水潦尘埃归焉。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=452&rangeEnd=506",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=452&rangeEnd=506"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_2228-2283",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2228-2283",
      "markText": "是故大丈夫恬然无思，澹然无虑。以天为盖，以地为舆，四时为马，阴阳为御。乘云陵霄，与造化者俱。纵志舒节，以驰大区",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2228&rangeEnd=2283",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2228&rangeEnd=2283"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_2548-2609",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2548-2609",
      "markText": "人生而静，天之性也，感而后动，性之害③也。物至神应，知之动也。知与物接而好憎生焉，好憎成形而知诱于外，不能反己，而天理灭矣",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2548&rangeEnd=2609",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2548&rangeEnd=2609"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_2024-2105",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2024-2105",
      "markText": "道这个东西，若有若无，不能详细描绘；似存似亡，但是用之不尽。视之不见，听之无声，深邃难测，但是动有所应。它遇到刚就展开，遇到柔就曲折，遇到阳就提高，遇到阴就降落。",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2024&rangeEnd=2105",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2024&rangeEnd=2105"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_5_356-408",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "356-408",
      "markText": "有始者，有未始有有始者，有未始有夫未始有有始者。有有者，有无者，有未始有有无者，有未始有夫未始有有无者。",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=356&rangeEnd=408",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=356&rangeEnd=408"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_4793-4831",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "4793-4831",
      "markText": "因此掌握了道的人，安安逸逸不会窘迫贫困，玩弄权术的人，辛苦忙碌也将一事无成。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=4793&rangeEnd=4831",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=4793&rangeEnd=4831"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_3075-3092",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "3075-3092",
      "markText": "故体道者逸而不穷，任数者劳而无功。",
      "totalCount": 135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=3075&rangeEnd=3092",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=3075&rangeEnd=3092"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_7349-7393",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "7349-7393",
      "markText": "得在时，不在争；治在道，不在圣；土处下，不争高，故安而不危；水下流，不争先，故疾而不迟。",
      "totalCount": 132,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=7349&rangeEnd=7393",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=7349&rangeEnd=7393"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_5_8640-8664",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "8640-8664",
      "markText": "是故道散而为德，德溢而为仁义，仁义立而道德废矣。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8640&rangeEnd=8664",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8640&rangeEnd=8664"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_2698-2714",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2698-2714",
      "markText": "以其无争于万物也，故莫敢与之争。",
      "totalCount": 121,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2698&rangeEnd=2714",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2698&rangeEnd=2714"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_590-644",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "590-644",
      "markText": "无为为之而合于道，无为言之而通乎德，恬愉无矜而得于和，有万不同而便于性。神托于秋毫之末，而大（于）宇宙之总。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=231443&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=590&rangeEnd=644",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f93321a0538813f9307fbdf?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=590&rangeEnd=644"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "231443_1_7607-7632",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "7607-7632",
      "markText": "所谓无为者，不先物为也；所谓无不为者，因物之所为。",
